| Column | Description |
|--------|-------------|
| **Rank** | Overall ranking by win rate across all player counts |

| **Set** | Expansion the alien is from (Base Game, Cosmic Incursion, etc.) |

| **3P** | Win rate in 3-player games (expected: 33%) |
| **4P** | Win rate in 4-player games (expected: 25%) |
| **5P** | Win rate in 5-player games (expected: 20%) |
| **6P** | Win rate in 6-player games (expected: 17%) |
| **Games** | Total number of games simulated with this alien |

*Note: Win rates above the expected value indicate stronger aliens for that player count.*
